OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Tony
OL,4,CRampling
OL,6,FTony Rampling, Age 99, Reconnaissance
OL,7,FRegiment
OL,9,FInterviewed 17 July 2023
OL,11,FDeparting from Southampton and
OL,12,Farriving a few days after the
OL,13,Finvasion, Tony Rampling landed with
OL,14,Fthe 61st Reconnaissance Regiment.
OL,16,FThey were tasked with scouting ahead
OL,17,Fand gathering tactical information for
OL,18,Finfantry soldiers.
