OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Tony
OL,4,CRampling
OL,6,F"We had the most horrendous time
OL,7,Fthere. We were actually hiding up in
OL,8,Fwoods on a hillside and the Jerries we
OL,9,Fwere cross firing at each other.
OL,11,F"Later on we started moving there was
OL,12,Fa long, straight road and two Jerries.
OL,13,FThey were Nazis because I could see
OL,14,Ftheir insignia. They ran across the
OL,15,Froad in front of us and I fired at
OL,16,Fthem and I am afraid I shot them.
OL,18,F"That's not very nice really but you
OL,19,Fhad to do it didn't you?"
